- **Workforce:** 0 FT employees; 6 contractors with no retention guarantees. Transition risk is critical.
- **Owner dependence:** Seller is central to operations. Post-sale support limited to "a few months."
- **Revenue model:** Custom manufacturing is inherently project-based and lumpy. No recurring revenue stream.
- **Industry:** Not in any of the 11 target acquisition verticals.
- **Customer concentration:** Unknown — could be materially concentrated.

